707764f-a.title: Manhattan: 2nd Ave. - 4th St.
707764f-a.text:
Second Avenue, west side, north from No. 73 adjoining the N.W.
corner of 4th Street.
June 25, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.

707763f-a.title: Manhattan: 2nd Ave. - 4th St.
707763f-a.text:
Second Avenue, west side, north from 4th Street, also showing some
of the east side. The spire at the right is that of the Middle
Collegiate Church adjoining the S.E. corner of 7th Street.
June 25, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
